          <title>La fisión binaria</title>
          <description><![CDATA[<p></p>

<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; float: left; width: 561.25px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">
<ul>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Tambi&eacute;n se denomina&nbsp;<strong>bipartici&oacute;n</strong></span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Es com&uacute;n en <strong>organismos unicelulares</strong></span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Genera un&nbsp;<strong>gran n&uacute;mero de individuos</strong> en poco tiempo</span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 23px;">La c&eacute;lula se&nbsp;<strong>alarga</strong> y <strong>duplica&nbsp;</strong>su contenido; despu&eacute;s&nbsp;se divide en dos y <strong>reparte equitativamente</strong> los componentes celulares entre las c&eacute;lulas hijas</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
</div>
]]></description>
