        <page i="0" visible="true" color="">
          <title>La esporulación</title>
          <description><![CDATA[<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; float: left; width: 561.25px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">
<ul>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Se caracteriza por la liberaci&oacute;n de&nbsp;<strong>esporas</strong> microsc&oacute;picas</span></span></li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">Las esporas contienen&nbsp;</span><strong style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">nutrientes </strong><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">y una copia exacta de la informaci&oacute;n del organismo que las produce</span></li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 23px;">El organismo libera esporas al medio, y en&nbsp;condiciones adecuadas,&nbsp;estas se convierten en <strong>nuevos organismos</strong></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
</div>
]]></description>
