          <title>Fisión / Regeneración</title>
          <description><![CDATA[<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; float: left; width: 561.25px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">
<ul>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Es propia de ciertos organismos <strong>multicelulares</strong></span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Se denomina <strong>fisi&oacute;n</strong> o <strong>escisi&oacute;n</strong> cuando el&nbsp;individuo se divide en <strong>dos partes</strong>, de manera accidental o no&nbsp;</span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 23px;">Se habla de <strong>fragmentaci&oacute;n</strong></span><span style="line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;si el organismo se divide en m&aacute;s de dos partes</span></span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">De cada fragmento se&nbsp;desarrolla un <strong>nuevo individuo</strong> y el organismo original <strong>regenera</strong> la parte perdida</span></span></li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; float: left; width: 561.25px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">
<p style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"></p>
</div>
]]></description>
