          <title>La partenogénesis</title>
          <description><![CDATA[<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; float: left; width: 561.25px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">
<ul>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Se presenta en algunos <strong>animales</strong></span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Genera&nbsp;nuevos individuos a partir de &nbsp;las <strong>c&eacute;lulas sexuales femeninas&nbsp;</strong></span></span><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 23px;">solamente</span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">En este tipo de reproducci&oacute;n <strong>no participan los machos</strong></span></span></li>
	<li style="border: 0px; outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Ciertos <span style="line-height: 23px;"><strong>factores ambientales</strong>&nbsp;</span>activan la c&eacute;lula sexual femenina induciendo su&nbsp;desarrollo hasta formar un nuevo organismo</span></span></li>
</ul>
</div>
]]></description>
